Police in Tsomo arrested a 24-year-old man for the alleged murder of an 80-year-old woman."It is alleged that the suspect was from the tarven at Mawusheni Location during the early hours of Saturday morning when he went to the deceased house, who is also related to him and stabbed the old woman," said police spokesperson, Capt Namhla Mdleleni. "The community heard the old woman screaming and when the community arrived they found the old woman in a pool of blood and sustained several wounds in her body and she died at the scene."Capt Mdleleni said that a case of murder has been opened and the suspect was arrested and will appear before Tsomo Magistrate's Court on Monday.